      "body" : "I suspect that this is being set erroneously given I'm getting 100% CPU pretty reliably and not when the patch is removed.\r\nhttps://github.com/pstratem/bitcoin/blob/3c08b7a23fe3afc8025658316b99f750c9a90fbf/src/main.cpp#L3980\r\nleaves vRecvMsg non-empty if the send buffer is full which will cause an infiniloop condition when a buffer fills up.",
